'''''Cladoceras''''' is a [[Monotypic taxon|monotypic]] [[genus]] of [[flowering plant]]s in the [[Family (biology)|family]] [[Rubiaceae]]. The genus contains only one [[species]], viz. '''''Cladoceras subcapitatum''''', which is [[Endemism|endemic]] to eastern [[Kenya]] and [[Tanzania]].<ref>Bremekamp, Cornelis Eliza Bertus. 1940.  Hooker's Icones Plantarum 35: , t. 3411. ''Cladoceras subcapitatum''</ref><ref>[https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/214304#page/544/mode/1up Schumann, Karl Moritz & Krause, Kurt. 1907.  Botanische Jahrbücher für Systematik, Pflanzengeschichte und Pflanzengeographie 39: 525, ''Chomelia subcapitata'']</ref><ref name="WCSP">[http://apps.kew.org/wcsp/namedetail.do?name_id=41378 Kew World Checklist of Selected Plant Families, ''Cladoceras subcapitatum'']</ref>

